d":41859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T08:40:14.000Z","msg":"問我咪得囉"},{"pid":"b0c5e3c8dcb16fc476faaec76110d9c6dcb1fe81","tid":109781,"uid":73706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T08:40:25.000Z","msg":"會比人妒忌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbf9de3300ac625bf978f51e5d5e2d498d5cc34f","tid":109781,"uid":64701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T08:41:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我淨係知做靚仔係咩feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最誇張試過俾個女仔及到唔睇路撞咗落我呀哥到<br />\n個陣佢係我隔離，我大佬唔算靚仔<br />\n<br />\n不過靚仔靚女唔係想像中咁好<br />\n例如個個一定以為自己有伴侶<br />\n又或者有對自己有興趣嘅女仔唔係因為內涵而接近自己<br />\n讀書時明明係我俾個女仔吸引，但個個同學同老師都係話個女仔痴上黎(嗰個女仔唔靚，真係好唔靚)<br />\n但佢因為自卑而拒絕拍拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成就都會歸咎於外型上，被人無視背後嘅努力"},{"pid":"b490d06cb31086969e257e8ba3c00242b6667be3","tid":109781,"uid":81880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T08:43:33.000Z","msg":"慣左 無乜特別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}